<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Main Page</title>
    <style>

        /* CSS Variables for Dark and Light Mode */
        :root {
            --bg-color: #f0f0f0; /* Light mode background */
            --text-color: #333; /* Light mode text color */
            --primary-color: #4CAF50; /* Primary buttons and headings color */
            --highlight-color: #f44336; /* Payment Due highlight color */
        }

        /* Basic Reset */
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        color: #333;
    }

    #Dashboard {
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h3 {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        color: #4CAF50;
    }

    p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .payment-info {
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #e9f5e9;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .payment-info strong {
        color: #4CAF50;
    }

    .payment-frame {
        border: 1px solid #4CAF50;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .form-group {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    label {
        font-weight: bold;
        flex-basis: 30%; /* Adjust as needed for label width */
    }

    /* Adjust Checkbox Wrapper */
    .checkbox-wrapper {
        display: flex;
        align-items:center;
        
    }

    input[type="checkbox"] {
        margin-right: 5px; /* Small margin between checkbox and label */
    }

    input[type="number"], 
    select {
        padding: 10px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 14px;
        width: 65%; /* Adjust for input width */
        transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }

     /* Highlight Amount Due */
     #amountDue {
        color: red; /* Highlight in red */
        font-weight: bold; /* Make it bold for emphasis */
    }

    input[type="number"]:focus, 
    select:focus {
        border-color: #4CAF50;
        outline: none;
    }

    button {
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #4CAF50; /* Constant color for buttons */
        color: rgb(8, 8, 8);
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 16px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    button:hover {
        background-color: #deb633;
    }

    .logout-btn {
        padding: 5px 10px; /* Smaller padding for a smaller button */
        font-size: 14px; /* Smaller font size */
        background-color: #f44336;
    }

    .logout-btn:hover {
        background-color: #d32f2f;
    }

    /* Responsive Styles */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        #Dashboard {
            padding: 15px;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        button {
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        input[type="number"], 
        select {
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .form-group {
            flex-direction: column; /* Stack inputs vertically on small screens */
        }

        label {
            flex-basis: auto; /* Reset for small screens */
            margin-bottom: 5px; /* Space between label and input */
        }

        input[type="number"], 
        select {
            width: 100%; /* Full width on small screens */
        }
    }

        

        
        /* Basic styling for the page */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Tab container styling */
        .tab-container {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        /* Tab button styling */
        .tab-button {
            background-color: #9cb8f5;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-right: 5px;
            outline: none;
        }

        .tab-button.active {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Tab content styling */
        .tab-content {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .tab-content.active {
            display: block;
        }

        /* Collapsible styling */
        .collapsible {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            color: #444;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            border: none;
            text-align: left;
            outline: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .collapsible::after {
            content: '\25B6'; /* Right-pointing arrow */
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #777;
            position: absolute;
            right: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .collapsible.active::after {
            transform: rotate(90deg); /* Downward-pointing arrow */
        }

        .collapsible.active, .collapsible:hover {
            background-color: #ccc;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 0 18px;
            display: none;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .lesson-content {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        /* Video styling */
        .video-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        video {
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 700px;
            height: auto;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        // Function to switch tabs
        function openTab(event, tabName) {
            const tabContents = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content');
            const tabButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');

            // Hide all tab contents and remove active class from all buttons
            tabContents.forEach(content => content.classList.remove('active'));
            tabButtons.forEach(button => button.classList.remove('active'));

            // Show the current tab content and add active class to the button
            document.getElementById(tabName).classList.add('active');
            event.currentTarget.classList.add('active');
        }

        // Function to toggle collapsible content
        function toggleCollapsible(event) {
            event.currentTarget.classList.toggle('active');
            const content = event.currentTarget.nextElementSibling;
            content.style.display = content.style.display === "block" ? "none" : "block";
        }

        // Set the default active tab
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            document.querySelector('.tab-button').click();

            // Add event listeners to collapsible elements
            const collapsibles = document.querySelectorAll('.collapsible');
            collapsibles.forEach(collapsible => {
                collapsible.addEventListener('click', toggleCollapsible);
            });
        });

        // Function to redirect to the Dashboard tab
        function redirectToDashboard() {
            // Simulate clicking the "Dashboard" tab button to switch tabs
            const dashboardTabButton = document.querySelector('.tab-button:nth-of-type(2)');
            if (dashboardTabButton) {
                dashboardTabButton.click();
            }
        }

         // Function to toggle sub-select options based on payment method
    function toggleSubSelect() {
        const paymentMethod = document.getElementById('payment-method').value;
        const cardOptions = document.getElementById('card-options');
        const cryptoOptions = document.getElementById('crypto-options');

        cardOptions.style.display = paymentMethod === 'card' ? 'none' : 'block';
        cryptoOptions.style.display = paymentMethod === 'crypto' ? 'block' : 'none';
    }

    function updateSubMethodOptions() {
    const paymentMethod = document.getElementById('paymentMethod').value;
    const subMethodSelect = document.getElementById('subMethod');

    // Clear existing options
    subMethodSelect.innerHTML = '';

    // Add new options based on selected payment method
    if (paymentMethod === 'card') {
        subMethodSelect.innerHTML += '<option value="credit card">Credit Card</option>';
        subMethodSelect.innerHTML += '<option value="debit card">Debit Card</option>';
    } else if (paymentMethod === 'crypto') {
        subMethodSelect.innerHTML += '<option value="USDT">USDT</option>';
        subMethodSelect.innerHTML += '<option value="BTC">BTC</option>';
        subMethodSelect.innerHTML += '<option value="ETH">ETH</option>';
        subMethodSelect.innerHTML += '<option value="SOL">SOL</option>';
    }
}

// Change display values to "Processing" on form submission
document.getElementById('paymentForm').addEventListener('submit', function() {
    document.getElementById('paidAmount').textContent = 'Processing';
    document.getElementById('amountDue').textContent = 'Processing';
});
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Welcome to the Main Page</h2>

    <div class="tab-container">
        <button class="tab-button" onclick="openTab(event, 'Courses')">Courses</button>
        <button class="tab-button" onclick="openTab(event, 'Dashboard')">Dashboard</button>
    </div>

    <div id="Courses" class="tab-content">
        <h3>Courses</h3>

        <!-- Collapsible for Available Courses -->
        <button class="collapsible">Available Courses</button>
        <div class="content">
            <!-- Nested Collapsible for Blockchain -->
            <button class="collapsible">Blockchain</button>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Here write intro to blockchain course</p>
                <div class="video-container">
                    <h4>Preview</h4>
                    <video controls>
                        <source src="https://codechain.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Untitled+video+-+Made+with+Clipchamp.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                        Your browser does not support the video tag.
                    </video>
                </div>

                <!-- Pricing Information -->
                <div class="pricing">
                    <p>Price: <s>$30</s> <span style="color: red;">50% off</span> - Now Payable: <strong>$15</strong></p>
                    <button onclick="redirectToDashboard()">Buy Now</button>
                </div>

                <!-- Sub-collapsible for each day -->
                <% const days = [
                    { day: 'Day 1', topic: 'Blockchain Basics', summary: 'Learn the fundamental principles behind blockchain technology, including decentralization, consensus, and immutability.', videoUrl: 'https://codechain.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Hansi+Shalika+_+Hankithi+Kawana+(%E0%B7%84%E0%B6%82%E0%B6%9A%E0%B7%92%E0%B6%AD%E0%B7%92+%E0%B6%9A%E0%B7%80%E0%B6%B1%E0%B7%8F)+_+The+Knockouts+_+The+Voice+Sri+Lanka.mp4' },
                    { day: 'Day 2', topic: 'Consensus Mechanisms', summary: 'Explore various consensus mechanisms such as Proof of Work and Proof of Stake, and understand their role in blockchain security.', videoUrl: 'https://codechain.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/One+Direction+-+Night+Changes+(Lyrics).mp4' },
                    { day: 'Day 3', topic: 'Blockchain Applications', summary: 'Learn about real-world applications of blockchain technology across different industries.', videoUrl: 'https://codechain.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Passenger+-+Let+Her+Go+(Lyrics).mp4' },
                    { day: 'Day 4', topic: 'Future of Blockchain', summary: 'Discuss the future trends and potential challenges that blockchain technology may face in the coming years.', videoUrl: 'https://codechain.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Piyamanne+(%E0%B6%B4%E0%B7%92%E0%B6%BA%E0%B6%B8%E0%B7%90%E0%B6%B1%E0%B7%8A%E0%B6%B1%E0%B7%9A)+-+Cover+by+Harsha+Maduranga+_+Abishek+Geethadewa+_+2022.mp4' }
                ]; %>
                <% days.forEach((dayItem, index) => { %>
                    <button class="collapsible"><%= dayItem.day %></button>
                    <div class="content">
                        <% const dayString = `day${index + 1}`; %>
                        <% const approvedRequest = approvedRequests.find(req => req.day === dayString); %>
                        <% if (approvedRequest) { %>
                            <div class="lesson-content" style="display: block;">
                                <h4>Topic: <%= dayItem.topic %></h4>
                                <p>Summary: <%= dayItem.summary %></p>
                                <div class="video-container">
                                    <video controls>
                                        <source src="<%= dayItem.videoUrl %>" type="video/mp4">
                                        Your browser does not support the video tag.
                                    </video>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <p>You have not been approved for this lesson yet. Please wait for admin approval.</p>
                            <form action="/request-lesson/<%= dayString %>" method="POST">
                                <button type="submit">Request Lessons for the Day</button>
                            </form>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="Dashboard" class="tab-content">
        <h3>Dashboard</h3>
        <p>Welcome, <%= userEmail %>!</p>
        <p>Here you can see an overview of your activities.</p>
    
        <div class="payment-info">
            <h3>Payment Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Paid Amount:</strong> <span id="paidAmount"><%= paidAmount || "no data" %></span></p>
            <p><strong>Amount Due:</strong> <span id="amountDue"><%= amountDue || "no data" %></span></p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Payment Form Frame -->
        <div class="payment-frame">
            <h3>Submit Payment</h3>
            <form action="/submit-payment" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="course">Course:</label>
                    <div class="checkbox-wrapper">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="course" value="blockchain" id="blockchain" required> 
                        <label for="blockchain">Blockchain</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="amount">Amount (in USD):</label>
                    <input type="number" name="amount" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="paymentMethod">Payment Method:</label>
                    <select name="paymentMethod" id="paymentMethod" required onchange="updateSubMethodOptions()">
                        <option value="card">Card</option>
                        <option value="crypto">Crypto</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="subMethod">Sub Payment Method:</label>
                    <select name="subMethod" id="subMethod" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected>Select a method</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <button type="submit">Submit Payment Request</button>
                <p>When you submit a payment request, within 24 hours you will receive a payment link and other payment details to your email. After your payment processed , it will be updated on your dashboard and you will be able to request lessons. You have to complete all due payments to request certificate and dgital badge.Minimum payment is 5 USD </p>
            </form>
        </div>

        <!-- Logout button inside Dashboard tab -->
    <form action="/logout" method="POST" style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <button type="submit" class="logout-btn">Logout</button>
    </form>
    
</body>
</html>
